160
00:10:38,119 --> 00:10:40,159
(But I can't risk your life.)

161
00:10:41,520 --> 00:10:42,559
(I'm sorry.)

162
00:10:43,359 --> 00:10:44,239
(Lin Muxuan,)

163
00:10:45,960 --> 00:10:47,520
(I'm now having
a strong poison in my body.)

164
00:10:49,239 --> 00:10:51,320
(Perhaps fate has destined
this part between us.)

165
00:10:53,919 --> 00:10:54,960
(For both you and me,)

166
00:10:56,719 --> 00:10:58,119
